          "notes": [],
          "synonyms": []
        },
        {
          "sn": "2.",
          "fields": [],
          "defs": [
            "Free from constraint or obligation; not bound by duty, habit, etc.; -- with from or of."
          ],
          "quotes": [
            "Now I stand Loose of my vow; but who knows Cato's thoughts ?"
          ],
          "notes": [],
          "synonyms": []
        },
        {
          "sn": "3.",
          "fields": [],
          "defs": [
            "Not tight or close; as, a loose garment."
